  ('medical-tech-moex-11358', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '某69歲男性，因員工健康檢查發現有貧血但沒有其他臨床症狀，經轉介至血液科門診複診。理學 檢查發現結膜微蒼白，沒有肝脾腫大。血液報告RBC=3.2×106/μL、Hb=9.6 g/dL、MCV=102 fL、reticulocyte 1.5%、WBC=6,500/μL；WBC 分類正常（segmented neutrophil 62%、 lymphocyte 30%）；血小板=240,000/μL；血液抹片觀察到neutrophil hypogranulation與pseudo Pelger-Huët cells；vitamin B 、folic acid及ferritin濃度皆正常，同時病患沒有服用任何中藥或西 12 藥；骨髓檢查結果：moderately hypercellularity、blast占2.4%，出現明顯dyserythropoiesis變 化；則推測最可能罹患下列何種疾病？', '["aplastic anemia", "paroxysmal nocturnal hemoglbinuria", "megaloblastic anemia", "myelodysplastic syndrome"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3fcca9e61875", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1b8f280795ba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103020", "c": "311", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第一次專技牙醫師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
